1
00:00:14,140 --> 00:00:14,750
Yuanji.

2
00:00:17,830 --> 00:00:18,760
You're here too.

3
00:00:19,830 --> 00:00:22,000
I have something
to report to His Highness.

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,800
Wuyi is injured from the caning.

5
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:25,580
Lady Xie is taking care of him.

6
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:29,120
Is it about Cui Jun kidnapping Lady Xie?

7
00:00:29,510 --> 00:00:32,170
Yes. I need to ask
His Highness for forgiveness.

8
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,920
I let Cui Jun go.

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,200
Even though the Empress Dowager
threatened me with my family,

10
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,430
I was wrong.

11
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:42,070
Jiayu was also taken away
by Cui Jun because of me

12
00:00:42,070 --> 00:00:43,470
and almost got into trouble.

13
00:00:43,470 --> 00:00:44,560
Wuyi already knew

14
00:00:45,060 --> 00:00:46,710
that you took Qing Long's key.

15
00:00:46,710 --> 00:00:47,470
What?

16
00:00:48,070 --> 00:00:49,730
The incident at Lingfeng Fort

17
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:51,520
can no longer be kept a secret.

18
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:54,640
The Phoenix Heart Tokens and the mine
have caught the noble families' attention.

19
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,430
They will definitely make a move.

20
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:58,670
The noble families have always
wanted to sabotage the reform.

21
00:00:58,670 --> 00:00:59,840
As soon as they find an opportunity,

22
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:01,240
they won't easily let go.

23
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:03,000
Wuyi had a premonition.

24
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:05,560
Since the Empress Dowager
has entered the game,

25
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,620
she won't be able to escape so easily.

26
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:08,789
His Highness

27
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:12,570
is going to make a move
against the Empress Dowager?

28
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:15,270
In that case, I should go find him.

29
00:02:41,510 --> 00:02:45,430
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

30
00:02:45,579 --> 00:02:48,380
[Episode 20]

31
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:50,610
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

32
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,960
What are you zoning out for?

33
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,800
Back then, to protect your child,

34
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,830
you broke ties with your family.

35
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,150
How did it feel?

36
00:03:08,910 --> 00:03:09,960
I was relieved.

37
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,750
They wanted me to be buried alive
with the dead.

38
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:12,880
What else could I do?

39
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,190
I wish I could be as decisive as you.

40
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:21,400
My father, brother,
and mother don't care about me,

41
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,260
willing to sacrifice my marriage

42
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:25,150
to surrender to the Empress Dowager.

43
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:28,079
But I can't just abandon them.

44
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:30,310
For so many years,

45
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,560
I've hidden in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

46
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,590
reading and studying,

47
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,920
pretending to be sober,

48
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,910
but actually just escaping.

49
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:40,910
His Highness gave me
the divorce paper long ago,

50
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:41,590
but I

51
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,030
dare not leave.

52
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:47,150
I followed my grandfather
to practice medicine from childhood

53
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:48,950
and found an interesting thing.

54
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:50,470
In practicing medicine,

55
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:51,470
it's often the poor

56
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:53,560
who are more willing to try harsh medicine
with a massive dosage.

57
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,560
One dose down

58
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,310
often leads to miraculous effects.

59
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:58,470
However, when people
from noble families get sick,

60
00:03:58,470 --> 00:03:59,750
they are always
careful with their medicine,

61
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:01,150
afraid of making mistakes,

62
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:03,120
which turns minor illnesses
into major ones.

63
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,000
Guess why?

64
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:06,840
Maybe because those who have less

65
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,850
are more willing to take risks.

66
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,520
However, those who grew up in luxury

67
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,520
are indebted to their families

68
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,850
and controlled by them,

69
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:19,160
having their wings broken
from the bottom of their hearts

70
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,560
and having too many scruples.

71
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:23,360
So it's normal that you
can't let go of your family.

72
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,350
Everyone is born different;

73
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:27,830
there's no need to live the same way.

74
00:04:31,130 --> 00:04:34,140
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

75
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,050
Your Highness.

76
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,540
Your Highness.

77
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:53,240
Move. I'm going to get
the imperial physician.

78
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,390
Her Majesty said

79
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,830
Prince Qi was injured

80
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,930
and needed rest.

81
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,360
The physician will arrive later.

82
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,780
Her Majesty...

83
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,000
Ruisheng, is his wound really okay?

84
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:10,750
Don't worry. The wounds he suffered before

85
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,750
were 10 or 100 times worse than this,

86
00:05:13,170 --> 00:05:14,100
and he survived.

87
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,240
But you can't just think

88
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,950
that because his previous wounds
were worse,

89
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:22,750
the current one doesn't matter.

90
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,000
Ruisheng,

91
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:25,790
please think of another way.

92
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,740
Rest assured,
I'll watch him drink his medicine,

93
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,510
without missing every single drop.

94
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:30,800
As for His Highness's medicine,

95
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,310
coptis is indeed missing.

96
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,680
I'll add it later.

97
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,780
Your Highness,

98
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:41,090
Chan, a maid in the Eastern Palace,

99
00:05:41,270 --> 00:05:42,120
who is Lady Xie's

100
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,920
dancer friend she saved before,

101
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,390
asked someone
to send out a bag of medicine residue.

102
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:47,960
Something is wrong with Prince Qi.

103
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,090
I'm afraid it's bad.

104
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:52,070
This is the only news
from the Eastern Palace recently.

105
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:53,070
How could that be?

106
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,700
Didn't they say
the arrow wound wasn't deep?

107
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:58,040
Was the arrow poisoned?

108
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,390
I had a wound on my palm

109
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,160
and touched the arrow that day.

110
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,620
If it were poisoned,
I would not be unharmed.

111
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:12,290
Check the medicine residue.

112
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,290
Something's wrong?

113
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,830
I remember now.

114
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:20,360
When I used to practice medicine
with my grandfather,

115
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,480
while gathering herbs in the mountains,

116
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,360
I came across an herb with a lily scent.

117
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,510
Its sprouts are poisonous.

118
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:26,600
When the poison acts up,
it looks like a normal high fever.

119
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,750
The fever continues until the person dies.

120
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:30,310
If a physician doesn't know
about this poison,

121
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:31,750
they won't be able to find the cause.

122
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:34,080
Usually, the patient dies without a cure.

123
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:36,310
Was Mao poisoned too?

124
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:36,920
Will he...

125
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,650
Don't worry.

126
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,220
This poison's symptoms are just hidden.

127
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:41,420
Its toxin can be neutralized with ease.

128
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:46,560
Don't worry.

129
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,510
I remember your grandfather

130
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,240
used to work
at the Imperial Medical Bureau.

131
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,750
Yes, but he retired early

132
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:56,950
and took me to practice medicine
among the people.

133
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:58,159
He passed away a few years later.

134
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,220
When did he retire?

135
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:01,510
About 13 years ago,

136
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,390
not long after His Majesty
ascended the throne.

137
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:07,720
High fever. Poisoning.

138
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,830
Immediately scout the guards
of the Eastern Palace

139
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:10,790
and the deployment
of the Imperial Guard again.

140
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:11,310
Yes.

141
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,280
I need you to do something for me.

142
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,120
Ruisheng, why don't we go over the wall?

143
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,120
I know a little lightness skill,

144
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,780
so I can carry you both inside.

145
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,890
[Qin]

146
00:07:32,730 --> 00:07:33,830
Imperial Physician Qin.

147
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:34,920
The old lady said,

148
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,240
Madam Ruisheng severed ties
with the Yu family long ago.

149
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:40,440
Madam Ruisheng hasn't visited
the Yu residence tonight.

150
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:49,680
Brother.

151
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,860
I need to return to the He Mansion.

152
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,950
I'll go with you.

153
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:09,430
Is it bitter?

154
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:12,210
I have pear blossom candy.

155
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:15,000
I like sour food.

156
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:18,390
Finish this today,

157
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:21,430
and I'll make you hawthorn cakes
another day.

158
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,120
Really?

159
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,830
No need. Just buy some hawthorns.

160
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,600
Making hawthorn cakes is too much trouble,

161
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,770
and peeling them hurts your hands.

162
00:08:41,669 --> 00:08:42,530
Your Highness.

163
00:08:43,549 --> 00:08:46,240
We've tried.
The Eastern Palace is indeed sealed off.

164
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,100
We can't get in.

165
00:08:47,210 --> 00:08:48,550
The Imperial Guard's
movements are abnormal.

166
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,200
The sentry rotation
at His Majesty's bedchambers

167
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,800
has ceased since last night.

168
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,600
The Empress Dowager
is trying to pull the same trick on Mao.

169
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:57,080
The Empress Dowager
has set this stage for so long.

170
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,610
It's time to put an end to it.

171
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,870
Go get my court attire.

172
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:08,000
Should you wear armor under it?

173
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,870
To deal with the Empress Dowager,

174
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:10,930
I don't need armor.

175
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,580
Your Highness, Prince Qi has been having
a fever for 2 days.

176
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:25,270
No one from the Imperial Medical Bureau
has come at all.

177
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:25,910
Ruisheng.

178
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,390
Tie up all the guards who have sealed off

179
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,420
the Eastern Palace in the past few days!

180
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,080
-Yes.
-Yes.

181
00:09:39,450 --> 00:09:40,020
Eunuch.

182
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:44,000
What happened?
Why are you in such a panic?

183
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,910
Y-Your Majesty,

184
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:46,550
Xiao Wuyi broke into
the Eastern Palace at night

185
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:47,930
to save His Highness Prince Qi.

186
00:09:47,930 --> 00:09:49,960
And Imperial Physician Qin was caught.

187
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,600
Will Imperial Physician Qin
reveal what happened—

188
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,730
Slap your own mouth.

189
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,600
I deserve to die.

190
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,390
I deserve to die.

191
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:55,240
I deserve to die.

192
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:55,720
I deserve to die.

193
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,390
Stop.

194
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,720
More than 20 people
in Imperial Physician Qin's family

195
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,790
are in my hands.

196
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:01,750
Even if he dies,

197
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:04,000
he won't dare to leak any information.

198
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,120
I guessed right.

199
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,870
We really can't let them

200
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:10,200
have the day
to turn the world upside down.

201
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:12,540
Since His Majesty won't listen to me,

202
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,630
I'll make the decision for him.

203
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:17,870
Pass on my decree.

204
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,010
Muster every man

205
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,670
of the Imperial Guard

206
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,960
who is from the He family.

207
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,670
Make them stop Xiao Wuyi for me.

208
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:24,240
Yes.

209
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,470
You know what to do.

210
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,360
Yes.

211
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:39,360
Today is a great day.

212
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,920
Arrange the Sun-Moon Phoenix coiffure

213
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:45,390
for me for this dynastic transition.

214
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,030
Yes.

215
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,840
Why hasn't His Majesty drunk it yet?

216
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,690
Please take your medicine, Your Majesty.

217
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,600
In this Jiankang Palace,

218
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,060
the only one who truly treats you well

219
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:55,390
is me.

220
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,240
Do you know how much effort I put in

221
00:11:58,910 --> 00:12:01,440
in exchange for your current status?

222
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:02,910
I

223
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,740
always remember your kindness, Mother.

224
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,030
In that case,

225
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:11,150
promise me 3 things tonight.

226
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,440
First,

227
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,550
stop the Beifu Reform.

228
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,320
Second,

229
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,580
abolish Prince Qi's position as Regent.

230
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:23,630
Third, as for the position
of Crown Prince,

231
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:26,870
I've found a suitable candidate for you.

232
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:30,560
The third son of Prince You.

233
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:33,310
What do you think, Your Majesty?

234
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:34,630
Mother,

235
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,870
what I think tonight

236
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,410
is no longer important.

237
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,440
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty.

238
00:12:56,500 --> 00:12:58,000
What is the meaning of this?

239
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,000
Qin Sheng murdered
Prince Qi and His Majesty.

240
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,390
He was caught red-handed.

241
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:03,840
There must be a mastermind behind it.

242
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:11,810
Qin Sheng, who told you to do this?

243
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,710
It was done by me alone.

244
00:13:12,690 --> 00:13:14,930
[Qin Sheng, Imperial Physician]

245
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,510
-Nuo.
-Father.

246
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,480
Father, why are you bleeding?

247
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,320
Does it hurt, Father?

248
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,120
Don't be afraid, Lord Qin.

249
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,680
All your kin are present.

250
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:41,140
Just tell us what you know.

251
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:48,030
Just speak.

252
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,870
I'll tell you. I'll tell you.

253
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,640
That was the winter 13 years ago.

254
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,800
Since coming south to Jiankang,

255
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:57,670
after Wenxi and her son
passed away one after another,

256
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,960
the late Emperor became ill from grief.

257
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:02,150
When it came time
to appoint the Crown Prince,

258
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,750
Prince Su and Prince Ning

259
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,300
were the hope of the court.

260
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:09,750
That night, it snowed heavily.

261
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:23,120
Take this prescription.

262
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,510
Mix it into the bird's nest soup
for a late-night snack

263
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:27,370
and send the soup to every prince.

264
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:29,530
Even your own flesh and blood,

265
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,720
Prince Yan, too?

266
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:33,850
To achieve our goal,

267
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:36,550
we must be willing to sacrifice.

268
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,390
I have my own way to protect my son.

269
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,600
Three months later,

270
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:44,270
Prince Su and Prince Ning
died one after another,

271
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:45,870
with only Prince Yan left alive.

272
00:14:45,870 --> 00:14:47,670
But Prince Yan was also poisoned

273
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:50,080
and became bedridden.

274
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,200
Nonsense!

275
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:53,150
His Majesty is my biological son.

276
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:55,030
How could I be so cruel as to harm him?

277
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:57,630
Qin Sheng, who put these words
into your mouth?

278
00:14:57,910 --> 00:15:00,320
Who asked you to frame me? Speak!

279
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:04,720
Mother.

280
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,730
I still remember that
in the bird's nest soup,

281
00:15:11,630 --> 00:15:13,630
there was a trace of lily scent.

282
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:15,190
The poison

283
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:20,320
was Dark Night Herb, right?

284
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:26,800
Take them away first.

285
00:15:39,220 --> 00:15:40,670
When did you know?

286
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:43,000
From the first day.

287
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,400
Then why did you still drink it?

288
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,240
Because since I was young,

289
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:54,120
I had always wanted to please you

290
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:58,550
and get your praise.

291
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:07,630
In that case,

292
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,840
do as I say tonight.

293
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:17,080
I cling to life

294
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,150
merely to get through each day.

295
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:22,600
I am an incompetent emperor

296
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:25,270
and an unfilial son.

297
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,480
No.

298
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,570
If you seek to contend and seize power,

299
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,660
I can't control it,

300
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,460
nor do I want to.

301
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,440
But if the Ye Empire

302
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,880
is really destroyed in my hands,

303
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:42,130
I will be too shameless
to face my ancestors.

304
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:50,600
Young Lord Xiao,

305
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,480
how is Prince Qi?

306
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:56,360
Your Majesty,
the poison has been neutralized.

307
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,480
He is resting now.

308
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,550
Xiao Wuyi,

309
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,589
do you think digging up old cases

310
00:17:06,589 --> 00:17:08,010
can put me to death?

311
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:09,550
I am the current Empress Dowager,

312
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:11,109
His Majesty's biological mother.

313
00:17:11,109 --> 00:17:13,000
So what if I did something wrong?

314
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:16,050
Besides, I have been waiting
for this moment tonight

315
00:17:16,050 --> 00:17:17,490
for a long time.

316
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,240
He Tian!

317
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:22,880
Xiao Wuyi conspired
to rebel in the palace.

318
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,680
Take him down!

319
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:42,790
Kneel.

320
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:46,460
-Greetings, Your Majesty.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

321
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:54,210
Greetings, Your Majesty.

322
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:57,210
Greetings, Your Majesty.

323
00:17:57,410 --> 00:17:58,130
Step back.

324
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:02,830
It's you.

325
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:06,240
You betrayed me.

326
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:11,350
Young Lord Xiao entered the palace tonight

327
00:18:11,350 --> 00:18:13,280
to bring down the Empress Dowager.

328
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:15,920
The He family kidnapped
Cui Jun for the Phoenix Heart Token

329
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:16,790
and instructed Cui Jun

330
00:18:16,790 --> 00:18:19,720
to sow discord
between Young Lord Xiao and Prince Qi.

331
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:21,440
After Cui Jun shot Prince Qi,

332
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:23,920
the Empress Dowager
secretly poisoned Prince Qi

333
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,440
to set up another Crown Prince.

334
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:26,880
The evidence is conclusive.

335
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,480
Then what are you doing here?

336
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,550
Why don't you hurry
and report to the Empress Dowager?

337
00:18:30,550 --> 00:18:33,200
Are you going to betray us?

338
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,880
We'll bring down
the Empress Dowager tonight,

339
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:37,480
and I also stand as a witness.

340
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:39,000
Young Lord Xiao has found out

341
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,400
the truth behind His Majesty's ascension.

342
00:18:41,550 --> 00:18:42,950
Prince Su and Prince Ning

343
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:45,000
were both poisoned by the Empress Dowager.

344
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,400
Tonight, trouble arises from within.

345
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,790
The He family has 2 choices.

346
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,990
First, cut off a finger to save the hand.

347
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:52,730
Second, die together
with the Empress Dowager.

348
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,110
Everyone,

349
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,880
do you want to live or die?

350
00:18:58,670 --> 00:18:59,670
What should we do?

351
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:01,750
If you want to live,

352
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:05,310
only I can protect the He family now.

353
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,680
What are you going to do?

354
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,200
Plead guilty

355
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:09,830
and support the Beifu Reform.

356
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:13,310
Absurd! The He family
is the top noble family in Jiangnan.

357
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:15,760
How could we support the reform?

358
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:18,790
Besides, the Empress Dowager
is His Majesty's mother.

359
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:20,400
Even if His Majesty knows

360
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:23,070
that the Empress Dowager
harmed Prince Su and Prince Ning,

361
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:24,550
he might not do anything.

362
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,360
What if the Empress Dowager

363
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,540
also poisoned His Majesty back then?

364
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:30,440
What if His Majesty is weak now

365
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,880
because the poison
wasn't completely cleared,

366
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,740
which leaves lingering effects?

367
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:35,790
I have married into
Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

368
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:37,520
I could have stayed out of this.

369
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:40,850
However, the He family
is my maternal clan after all.

370
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:43,110
So I still came tonight.

371
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,200
Will you continue to follow
the Empress Dowager's sinking ship

372
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,270
and drown together,

373
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:47,920
or listen to me from now on

374
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,300
and change course?

375
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:52,480
At least, we can keep the He family safe.

376
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,830
Choose for yourselves.

377
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,430
The family seal is here.

378
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,920
Very well.

379
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,920
This is the list I've collected
over the years

380
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:27,990
of the He family's forming factions

381
00:20:28,030 --> 00:20:29,310
and taking bribes.

382
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:31,350
Please review it, Your Majesty.

383
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:33,480
He Yuanji, are you crazy?

384
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:35,920
Are you trying to destroy the He family?

385
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:39,240
Aunt, I'm saving the He family.

386
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:41,920
The He family can't keep making mistakes.

387
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,120
Saving the He family?

388
00:20:44,790 --> 00:20:47,440
The He family moved south from Capital

389
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,720
to help establish the capital in Jiankang.

390
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,590
They have all made great contributions.

391
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:54,590
I beg for mercy;
do not implicate the entire He family.

392
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:08,240
Reform is the trend of the times,

393
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:11,090
not the slaughter of noble families.

394
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:13,240
If there are those who work together,

395
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,840
they should be granted grace

396
00:21:15,030 --> 00:21:16,160
and set as examples.

397
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,800
What about the Empress Dowager?

398
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:24,290
The Empress Dowager is old and confused.

399
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:26,550
Her seal should be confiscated,

400
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,030
and she should be moved to another palace

401
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:31,160
to spend her remaining years in peace.

402
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:46,280
Granted.

403
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:51,850
Granted?

404
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:55,730
Granted?

405
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:57,340
Guards.

406
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:59,140
My son.

407
00:22:00,150 --> 00:22:00,950
Let go!

408
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:06,510
My son, I did it all for you.

409
00:22:16,950 --> 00:22:18,560
When I got the family seal,

410
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,500
my grandfather told me

411
00:22:20,690 --> 00:22:22,310
that for the future
of the entire He family,

412
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:23,770
anyone can be sacrificed,

413
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:26,710
including his daughter.

414
00:22:26,830 --> 00:22:27,510
Aunt.

415
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,790
Your father and son

416
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:32,520
have already given up on you.

417
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:38,000
Do you think you can stay out of it?

418
00:22:52,550 --> 00:22:53,350
Your Majesty,

419
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:54,750
I, He Yuanji,

420
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:57,110
was granted a marriage
to Young Lord Xiao by the Empress Dowager.

421
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,350
We have been married for 5 years.

422
00:22:58,350 --> 00:22:59,880
My virtue and conduct are flawed.

423
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,210
I beg you, Your Majesty,

424
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:03,550
to annul the marriage
between the Xiao and He families

425
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:05,950
and allow me
and Young Lord Xiao to divorce.

426
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:09,090
I am willing to lead
the He family to support his reform.

427
00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:09,960
Granted.

428
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:15,440
The noble familie
are deeply rooted and intertwined.

429
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:17,680
Even my throne was given to me by them.

430
00:23:18,450 --> 00:23:19,580
You shall do

431
00:23:21,630 --> 00:23:23,020
what I can't for me.

432
00:23:25,070 --> 00:23:27,920
Xiao Wuyi, I will issue a secret edict.

433
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:29,720
If I die one day,

434
00:23:30,830 --> 00:23:32,790
let the Empress Dowager go with me,

435
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:35,590
lest she exploit filial piety as an excuse

436
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:37,030
to usurp power.

437
00:23:37,270 --> 00:23:38,000
Today,

438
00:23:39,550 --> 00:23:42,440
you covered up
the past court scandal for me

439
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:45,680
and saved the royal family's dignity.

440
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:48,400
I will play the villain
for you on another day.

441
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:54,460
I thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

442
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:57,790
Prince Qi, Li Mao.

443
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:00,880
I am here.

444
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:03,510
I bestow upon you the Nine Imperial Seals.

445
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,950
In the future, when you act on my behalf,

446
00:24:07,110 --> 00:24:09,310
you do not need to ask for instructions.

447
00:24:10,310 --> 00:24:11,710
Thank you, Your Majesty.

448
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,790
You shall preside

449
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,720
as chief judge over the Cui Family Case.

450
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,590
I receive the decree.

451
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:48,110
I won.

452
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:54,400
Congratulations, Mao,

453
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:57,270
on successfully bringing down
the Empress Dowager

454
00:24:57,270 --> 00:24:59,330
and getting the Nine Imperial Seals.

455
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:06,350
You did what Xiao Wuyi

456
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,240
couldn't do.

457
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:19,650
Are you leaving?

458
00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:30,640
Li Lejun no longer exists in this world.

459
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:31,550
Mao,

460
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:36,170
I will not become your stain.

461
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,720
You are not my stain.

462
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:47,030
You are my only family.

463
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:07,000
Your Highness,
why do you think I will help you?

464
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:10,550
If I tell Young Lord Xiao that

465
00:26:10,580 --> 00:26:11,910
Cui Jun is in the palace,

466
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:14,220
how do you think things will turn out?

467
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,240
If you really can't hide him,

468
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:18,790
in the end,

469
00:26:19,230 --> 00:26:20,990
won't it still be your fault?

470
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:25,720
Even if I am sacrificed,

471
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:28,830
Her Majesty won't suffer any loss.

472
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,420
Why would I sacrifice you?

473
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:33,010
What do you want me to do?

474
00:26:33,790 --> 00:26:34,720
Release Cui Jun,

475
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:36,920
take Xie Jiayu hostage,

476
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:38,560
and have him shoot me.

477
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:40,520
That's true.

478
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:43,070
The incident with Li Lejun

479
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:45,670
alienated you
from Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

480
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,000
If Her Majesty

481
00:26:47,410 --> 00:26:48,960
really wants to kill you,

482
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:51,880
she won't stop easily.

483
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,240
You also want

484
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:02,350
Her Majesty and Xiao Wuyi
to fight each other.

485
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:05,350
I heard you have a nephew,

486
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:07,450
whom you treat as your own son.

487
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,440
Back then, you wanted to use the He family

488
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:11,240
to secure an official career for him.

489
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,100
Unexpectedly,

490
00:27:12,240 --> 00:27:14,270
he was led by the worthless sons
of the He family

491
00:27:14,270 --> 00:27:16,230
to drink and make merry all day,

492
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:18,270
and almost became a useless person.

493
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:20,830
His Majesty's chronic illness
is now hard to cure.

494
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:22,120
How many more years do you think

495
00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:24,450
the Empress Dowager will remain in power?

496
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:26,000
Why not

497
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:28,420
form a good tie with me?

498
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:49,110
Wuyi.

499
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,400
Thank you for your help today.

500
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,940
If you hadn't brought
Imperial Physician Qin,

501
00:27:53,940 --> 00:27:56,160
the Empress Dowager might have succeeded.

502
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:58,490
Xie Jiayu has already gone after Li Lejun.

503
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:11,850
Lejun.

504
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,180
Hope you've been well.

505
00:28:22,910 --> 00:28:24,030
I originally thought the Antai Gate

506
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:25,030
was the Empress Dowager's doing.

507
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:26,290
It turned out to be you,

508
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,680
constantly using her and me

509
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:30,280
to create chaos in Jiankang.

510
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:33,400
As long as the defense battalion's
troops are mobilized

511
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,720
and the Court of Judicial Review's
guard is down,

512
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:37,240
you could find an opportunity
to swap out Li Lejun

513
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,770
and send her out of the city.

514
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:40,830
But at least, I helped you
get rid of the Empress Dowager.

515
00:28:40,830 --> 00:28:41,890
Is that not enough?

516
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,350
Right and wrong,
and the bottom line of human life—

517
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:45,610
I understand them all.

518
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:48,070
But Li Lejun will always be my exception.

519
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:50,240
So I left the choice to Xie Jiayu.

520
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,560
Xiao Wuyi, you are too cruel,

521
00:28:55,030 --> 00:28:56,640
to both me and Xie Jiayu.

522
00:28:57,200 --> 00:29:00,240
Do you think she'll be able
to let it go if she kills Lejun?

523
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:00,830
No.

524
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:04,080
It will only make it harder
for her to face.

525
00:29:04,350 --> 00:29:06,010
I secretly swapped Lejun out,

526
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:07,310
then she can survive,

527
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:09,030
and Xie Jiayu would think
she has gotten her revenge.

528
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:10,110
Isn't that the best arrangement?

529
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,840
You underestimated Xie Jiayu.

530
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,800
She's not that easily defeated.

531
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,480
She can make a choice.

532
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:17,550
And this choice

533
00:29:18,530 --> 00:29:19,970
can only be made by her.

534
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:21,830
Jiayu,

535
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:25,110
there was no personal grudge
between Princess Yunzhao and me—

536
00:29:25,110 --> 00:29:26,510
only political rivalry.

537
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:27,710
I had no other choice.

538
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:29,650
Give me a reason not to kill you.

539
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:32,590
Fine.

540
00:29:33,830 --> 00:29:34,750
Then today,

541
00:29:36,030 --> 00:29:37,760
I will avenge my mother myself.

542
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,070
If Mao finds out,

543
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:40,920
he won't let you go.

544
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,690
Then let him come to me himself.

545
00:29:44,050 --> 00:29:45,380
I can go to Northern Qin.

546
00:29:46,070 --> 00:29:47,870
The Eagle King wants to marry me.

547
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:49,920
I can use this

548
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:52,570
and go undercover in Northern Qin.

549
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:55,900
Cui Jun went undercover in Ye
for Northern Qin for 20 years.

550
00:29:56,010 --> 00:29:56,940
If he could do it,

551
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:58,790
I can too.

552
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,200
Mao is the Regent.

553
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:03,510
If I go undercover in Northern Qin,

554
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:05,070
you can trust my loyalty.

555
00:30:05,590 --> 00:30:06,510
I'll be a spy

556
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:08,920
to help Mao realize his ambitions

557
00:30:09,270 --> 00:30:12,030
and keep Xiao Wuyi informed
of Northern Qin's movements.

558
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:14,000
Besides, being a spy
is extremely dangerous.

559
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,440
Even if I'm killed
by the Northern Qin people,

560
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:17,840
it won't be by your hands.

561
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,400
Jiayu.

562
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:23,960
We are friends.

563
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,000
I don't want

564
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,960
you to kill me with your own hands.

565
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,220
Let's leave it to fate.

566
00:30:49,610 --> 00:30:51,070
Xiao Wuyi, let me tell you,

567
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,240
from now on,

568
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:54,240
there is no brotherhood between us.

569
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:01,460
Only a bond of sovereign and subject.

570
00:31:50,070 --> 00:31:50,930
What happened?

571
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,060
Did Mao hit you?

572
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:54,950
I'm sorry.

573
00:31:55,550 --> 00:31:56,480
Don't overthink it.

574
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,940
This is between him and me.

575
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,300
-It's all my fault.
-Alright.

576
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:00,920
I'm fine.

577
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,550
Xiao Wuyi.

578
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,830
Although I said

579
00:32:13,110 --> 00:32:14,970
I didn't want to be a demon's wife,

580
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,680
but a hero's wife,

581
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:20,830
actually, I'm not afraid of

582
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:23,520
being condemned and notorious.

583
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:28,550
Why don't you ask me

584
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,460
if I did anything to Lejun?

585
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:34,970
Are you okay?

586
00:32:38,030 --> 00:32:40,310
She said she wanted
to go to Northern Qin as a spy

587
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:42,110
and stay undercover
by the Eagle King's side.

588
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:43,160
I shot an arrow.

589
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,310
Li Lejun.

590
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,120
We shall never meet again

591
00:32:57,510 --> 00:32:58,440
in this life.

592
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,020
If we do meet again,

593
00:33:01,750 --> 00:33:03,610
I will definitely take your life.

594
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:11,180
Take her to Northern Qin.

595
00:33:11,180 --> 00:33:11,700
Yes.

596
00:33:25,750 --> 00:33:27,750
Princess Yunzhao will understand.

597
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:06,170
Congratulations, Your Highness,
on taking full control of Jiankang.

598
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:08,670
Has the Empress Dowager departed yet?

599
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:10,400
The Empress Dowager
suffered an attack of intense anger,

600
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,630
was invaded by pathogenic wind,

601
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:12,560
and had a stroke.

602
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:14,670
She can hardly get up now.

603
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,920
The seal has been taken back.

604
00:34:17,190 --> 00:34:18,510
Early or late,

605
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:20,449
she still has to leave.

606
00:34:20,670 --> 00:34:23,960
Your Highness,
the Empress Dowager has truly fallen ill.

607
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:32,489
Then let her rest and recuperate.

608
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:35,880
About the matter you promised me before...

609
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,120
Your nephew is smart.

610
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:43,230
I have promoted him
to Commander of the Imperial Guard.

611
00:34:43,230 --> 00:34:44,690
Thank you, Your Highness.

612
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:47,000
As for you,

613
00:34:49,030 --> 00:34:50,630
stay in the temporary palace

614
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:53,000
and look after the Empress Dowager.

615
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,710
I... this...

616
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:13,660
The winner is decided.

617
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:16,260
Now that you are
the head of the He family,

618
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:18,550
why come here to show off your power?

619
00:35:19,070 --> 00:35:21,330
I remember when I was young and studying,

620
00:35:22,070 --> 00:35:23,870
Father and Mother always told me

621
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,200
that I had a very beautiful aunt.

622
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:29,870
She was a noble lady in Jiankang Palace.

623
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:32,410
She was beautiful, gentle,

624
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:34,500
and extremely intelligent.

625
00:35:34,590 --> 00:35:36,510
She excelled in the Four Arts.

626
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:40,320
She was especially good at
playing the ruanxian.

627
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:43,800
A piece of "Partridge" would make people
forget all worldly worries.

628
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:44,670
Father and Mother

629
00:35:44,670 --> 00:35:46,710
pointed at her portrait and told me

630
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:49,000
that a noble daughter
of an aristocratic family

631
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,200
with elegant bearing

632
00:35:50,230 --> 00:35:51,360
should be like this.

633
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:55,340
So I imitated her appearance
in the painting

634
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:57,590
to read,

635
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:00,210
practice calligraphy,

636
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:01,740
play the guqin,

637
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:03,840
and grow up,

638
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:07,300
wanting to become the second her.

639
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:10,840
Now,

640
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:16,960
can you still play?

641
00:36:26,630 --> 00:36:28,280
Later, I met that aunt.

642
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,920
I even brought my ruanxian that day.

643
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:34,460
But the first thing
she told me when she saw me

644
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:37,150
was that I needed
to marry a man I had never met

645
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:39,230
for the sake of the family.

646
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:42,190
Which noble lady

647
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,150
doesn't marry a man

648
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:45,480
she has never met?

649
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:49,240
But I had already agreed,

650
00:36:50,710 --> 00:36:52,950
and Pei Runheng was already dead!

651
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:55,760
Why did you have to frame them

652
00:36:56,230 --> 00:36:58,160
and destroy the entire Pei family?

653
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,400
Why?

654
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:03,190
It became a habit.

655
00:37:06,990 --> 00:37:09,880
The Pei family refused to believe
their son died in an accident.

656
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,920
How could I let them keep digging

657
00:37:12,630 --> 00:37:14,090
and causing more trouble?

658
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:32,710
When Runheng's mother committed suicide
with her daughter,

659
00:37:32,710 --> 00:37:35,110
his younger sister
was not even 5 years old!

660
00:37:36,540 --> 00:37:37,310
Aunt.

661
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:40,290
Because of your own lust for power,

662
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:42,480
how many lives have you ruined?

663
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:44,090
Lust for power?

664
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:46,160
Who is born with a lust for power?

665
00:37:46,210 --> 00:37:48,290
The He family ruined my life as well.

666
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,690
Who will cry foul for me?

667
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:51,030
Without me,

668
00:37:51,150 --> 00:37:52,230
the He family would be nothing

669
00:37:52,230 --> 00:37:53,760
but an insignificant clan.

670
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:55,710
All the wealth and glory you enjoy now

671
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:57,440
were bought with my sacrifice.

672
00:37:57,880 --> 00:38:00,400
What? Now that you're done using me,

673
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:03,350
you want to wash your hands of it?

674
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:08,510
But your luck is better than mine
after all.

675
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:10,610
Prince Jing'an's Mansion

676
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:13,480
is not the man-eating Jiankang Palace.

677
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:31,030
It's all an illusion.

678
00:38:32,430 --> 00:38:34,030
Old friends are not the same.

679
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,080
You probably don't know yet.

680
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:39,190
His Majesty

681
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:42,410
has already issued a secret edict.

682
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,550
The day he passes away

683
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:50,670
will be the day you die.

684
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:53,530
The future of the He family

685
00:38:56,170 --> 00:38:58,770
has absolutely nothing
to do with you anymore.

686
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:15,260
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

687
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:22,170
Cui Jun died without entering
the Court of Judicial Review.

688
00:39:22,230 --> 00:39:24,360
Whether he was truly a Northern Qin spy

689
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:28,110
or he fabricated the unjust case
involving the An and Lu families

690
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:30,510
can no longer be verified.

691
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:35,000
What about the Phoenix Heart Token?

692
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:36,770
It is with His Majesty.

693
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:01,230
Crown Prince Wenxi.

694
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:04,880
It has been returned
to its rightful owner.

695
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:08,110
Are you sure Xiao Wuyi

696
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,740
is Crown Prince Wenxi?

697
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,630
He definitely is.

698
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,150
I...

699
00:40:17,190 --> 00:40:18,590
I didn't know you knew...

700
00:40:19,150 --> 00:40:20,550
Let it be.

701
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:24,590
It is a blessing not to know.

702
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:29,890
I don't have many days left to live.

703
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,720
And I no longer have the will

704
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:37,230
to save the people of this world.

705
00:40:37,920 --> 00:40:40,380
I don't want to deal with
this massive flood,

706
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:42,550
and I can't anyway.

707
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:45,840
Are you just going to leave it be?

708
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:50,630
Crown Prince Wenxi's Phoenix Heart Token

709
00:40:50,630 --> 00:40:52,320
originally belonged to him.

710
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:56,360
I will use my own way

711
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:57,510
to beat him.

